晉級到十六強，、\n就可能要跟「Afterglow」對戰了吧……？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":26,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":26,"voiceId":"event212-06-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":28}],"windowDisplayName":"七深","body":"還可能，也會遇上「RAS」……？\n真沒想到我們認識的樂團也有參賽","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":28,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":28,"voiceId":"event212-06-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"windowDisplayName":"瑠唯","body":"３次戰還沒開始，\n現在討論以後的事也沒有幫助","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":30,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"event212-06-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":30}],"windowDisplayName":"瑠唯","body":"現在就先好好專注做好眼前的事吧。\n十六強的事，就等到順利在３次戰脫穎而出後再談吧","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":30,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":30,"voiceId":"event212-06-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":29}],"windowDisplayName":"筑紫","body":"也，也是。畢竟下次的對手，一定也很厲害……\n得好好專心才行！","tention":0,"lipSyn